nslationLine"></p></div>			<! Question 4>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>4. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;毎日&nbsp;&nbsp;	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('はやく',this.value,3)" style="width: 150px;">    </INPUT>ねなければいけません。[早い]	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>				<! Question 5>	<div class="questionLineOdd"><b>5. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;今日は&nbsp;&nbsp;		<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('おそく',this.value,4)" style="width: 150px;">	</SELECT>起きたので、がっこうに行きませんでした。[おそい]	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>	<! Question 6>	<div class="questionLineEven"><b>6. </b>&nbsp;&nbsp;スペイン語が	<INPUT name="answer" type="text" onChange="checkAnswer('じょうずに',this.value,5)" style="width: 150px;">    </INPUT>話せません。[じょうず]	<IMG SRC="../../../gimages/blank.gif" class="symbols">	<p class="translationLine"></p></div>			</FORM><div id="score"></div><div><table class="optionBox"><tr>	<td><BUTTON onClick="checkAnswers()">Check Answers</BUTTON></td>	<td><BUTTON onClick="resetValues()">Reset Values</BUTTON></td></tr></table></div></div></body></html>